title: Teleatlas Polska Czechy 2008 2009 Blaupunkt TravelPilot Navigati
description:
The Blaupunkt TravelPilot Czech Republic - Poland + Major Roads of Europe maps show: 

Product Highlights


~100% detailed street network for Czech Republic available. 
Extended door-to-door route guidance in the Czech Republic and Poland: ~26% of the Czech and ~47% of the Polish population can now be reached by selection of house number ranges!
This product has been extended by over 200.000 km!
Updated official TMC code list for Czech Republic improves dynamic route guidance on Czech motorways.*
Feeling hungry, need to find a parking spot or want to top up on fuel? Count on around 128 750 Points of Interest (POI) such as restaurants and car parks. Including 11 750 new destinations such as: city centres, hotels, restaurants, government offices and petrol stations with CNG and LPG.
*Availability depends on the navigation system


Blaupunkt TravelPilot Czech Republic - Poland + Major Roads of Europe is compatible with: 

DX-V, DX-N, DX-R 5, DX-R 52, DX-R 70, DX-R 4, RNS 4
